        <div class="span5 copy">
          <p>
            Social studio is an online, collaborative music studio. Musicians can
            upload individual instrument tracks for others to use to record their own
            tracks against. Collaboratively entire pieces of music can be created and
            endlessly remixed.
          </p>
          <p>Completed tracks can be mixed down and put up for sale, the proceeds from which
          go to the artists.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid section2">
        <div class="span5 offset1 copy copy-right">
          <p>Features of The Social Studio: </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Contribute as many tracks as you want, with whatever instruments you need.</li>
            <li>Use any number of tracks as basis for your own track.</li>
            <li>Record your own track over these for you or someone else to use to create a final song.</li>
            <li>Use an online mixer to mix these down to a final song.</li>
            <li>Make music with highly talented, original artists.</li>
            <li>Profit.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="span5 asset">
          <img class="img-polaroid" src="http://placehold.it/480x300">
